#

Crispy Herb-Crusted Chicken with Garlic Mashed Potatoes and Green Beans

$20.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carbohydrate

Tags:

PopularComfort FoodAmerican Cuisine

Description

Juicy chicken breast coated in a crispy herb crust, served with creamy garlic mashed potatoes and fresh green beans.

Ingredients

  • Chicken breast: 4 pieces
  • Panko breadcrumbs: 1 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup
  • Dried oregano: 2 tsp
  • Garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Milk: 1/2 cup
  • Fresh green beans: 1 lb
